snippet.title: IMMURE Demo - Dev Log
snippet.description:
Developer log for IMMURE, a psychological horror game currently in development by Wither Studios.

Please check out our current Kickstarte Campaign: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/witherstudios/immure-inescapable-horror

In this video, one of our developers talks over some pre-cut gameplay footage of an earlier build for the demo. Various game mechanics are talked about as well as our thought process for different sections of the game.
